name: Vintage / 1960's Crystal Collar Statement Necklace
description:
A stunning vintage design, this necklace is shaped to look like a little dress collar. It sits beautifully on the neck to highlight your collar bone.

Bright and sparkly, in great condition. Approx 15" in length but can be worn shorter as the clasp just hooks over the crystal of your choice.

name: Vintage / Tiered Metal Jewellery Stand
description:
This is a gorgeous one for a dressing table!

A sweet little metal jewellery stand, it looks like a cake stand but is actually a much smaller version made to hold jewellery. The bottom plate is approx 6" in diameter and the top plate is approx 4" in diameter.

A great unusual way to keep your jewellery safe. The stand is engraved all over which is very attractive to look at, and the silver tone would compliment a lot of themes (Parisian would be lovely).

In great condition. Dismantles for easy posting.

name: Vintage Style / Jewellery Range Swallow and Pearl Necklace
description:
A bronze tone necklace with a large swallow bird pendant, the swallow is carrying a pearl bead in it's beak.

The chain on this one is approx 20" long

name: Vintage / Sterling Silver Enamel Heart Necklae
description:
A pretty sterling silver necklace with a large heart pendant. The heart pendant is set with 3 smaller hearts which are enameled in pastel pink, blue and green.

A quality necklace fully hallmarked 925. In lovely condition. The chain is 15" long with a 3.5" extension and the pendant is approx 3.3 cms tall.

name: Vintage / Crystal Musical Note Brooch
description:
A beautiful silver tone musical note brooch set with clear crystals. A great gift for a musician to pin to their jacket or instrument bag!

Approx 5.6 cms in height and in perfect condition.

name: Vintage / Coral Orchid Necklace
description:
This necklace was up-cycled by myself from a single vintage clip on earring. The pendant is a a beautiful orchid flower covered in tiny polished coral stones.

As this is an up-cycled vintage piece, it's completely one of a kind and there has only ever been one made.

The chain is approx 18" long and the pendant is 2.5 cms tall including the bail. In lovely condition.

name: Vintage / Dainty Silver Tone Earrings
description:
A choice of 2 dainty sets of vintage earrings.

These ones look to be silver plated. There is some faint signs of gold showing though in places which actually looks very pretty. They are very fine and light.

Each earring is approx 3.2 cms tall from the top of the hook to the bottom of the design.

One pair is shaped like a leaf (left), and the other pair like a tear drop (right).

name: Vintage / Fine Gold and Turquoise Necklace
description:
Fine and dainty, this necklace looks to be gold plated. The chain is a weave design and silky to the touch.

It is accented with small round turquoise beads and gold spacer beads. Such a pretty design.

Approx 16" long and in lovely condition.

name: Vintage / Engraved Heart Locket
description:
A sweet vintage gold plated heart locket necklace. 

The little heart is engraved with flowers on the front and a shell type pattern on the back, it opens up and you can place two little photos inside.

The chain on this one is 16" with a 2.5" extension chain. The locket itself is approx 2.5 cms tall including the bail. In lovely condition.

name: Vintage Style / Sterling Silver Moons and Stars Necklace
description:
A dreamy modern necklace consisting of a central circle with a mobile of hanging crescent moons and stars. 

Marked 925, this one is a nice bright silver. There are 3 stars and 3 moons which all hang at different lengths for a really lovely layered effect.

The chain is approx 19" long with a 2" extension, and pendant is approx 7 cms from the top of the circle to the bottom of the lowest charm.

name: Vintage / Galleon Ship Brooch
description:
A beautiful silver tone brooch depicting a galleon (Pirate?) ship. A very elegant brooch that is quite lightweight and would be easily worn on a day to day basis.

Approx 3.6 x 4.5 cms in size. In perfect condition.

name: Vintage / Sterling Silver Mother of Pearl Heart Necklace
description:
Stunning vintage necklace made up entirely of mother of pearl hearts. A really unusual piece.

The hearts seem to be strung on wire, and the necklace is finished with a twist clasp to make getting it on and off easier. The hearts shine in a lovely pearly white/cream colour.

The necklace is just under 16" in length. It is is good condition with no damage. The hearts do not all want to sit in the same direction due to the wire being slightly twisted with age. Still a gorgeous statement piece!

name: Vintage / Sterling Silver Lapis Lazuli Gemstone Necklace
description:
A beautiful sterling silver necklace with a large statement stone pendant. The stone is a purple/blue colour with grey areas and silver flecks - truly beautiful.

The pendant is a circular shape, it is polished smooth and striking in it's minimalism. The pendant is approx 5 cms in height.

The chain is marked 925 and approx 24" long. In lovely condition.

name: Vintage / Sterling Silver Dainty Turquoise Medallion Necklace
description:
A lovely little necklace with a tiny turquoise set medallion pendant. A real nod to Native American work. 

The pendant is approx 1.8 cms tall and is on an 18" chain. Both are hallmarked 925 and in lovely condition.

name: Vintage Style / Sterling Silver Crystal Heart Ring
description:
A beautiful ring, marked 925.

Set with a deep pink crystal heart, very striking against the silver. A stunning design.

Size P

name: Vintage Style / Sterling Silver Modernistic Necklace
description:
A beautiful modernistic sterling silver necklace. Simple and beautiful.

The pendant is an elegant rain drop shape (approx 3.5 cms tall) and is on an 18" chain.

Still in it's original gift box, brand new and never worn. Perfect to give as a present.

name: Vintage / Leaping Leopard Brooch
description:
A gorgeous vintage brooch, this one is a leaping/running leopard. He has such a sweet face!

In lovely condition with just minor wear, approx 8.5 cms long. A great brooch to pin to a handbag!

name: Vintage / Sterling Silver Magic Lamp Necklace
description:
Lovely vintage 1970's necklace with a tiny magic lamp pendant.

The magic lamp opens to reveal a tiny genie inside!

Sterling silver, the pendant is approx 2.5 cms long including the bail. The chain is 20" long and marked 925. In great condition.

name: Vintage Style / Hummingbird Trinket Dishes
description:
6 beautiful little trinket dishes, each decorated with a stunning hummingbird pattern. Each of the 6 has a different pattern with a different breed of hummingbird.

Just missing out on their vintage status by 1 month (these ones were made in 1994, 1 month short of the 20 years required to be vintage) these little dishes are in perfect condition.

Lovely to put on a dresser or in a bathroom to keep earrings and rings safe. Each dish is approx 9.2 cms in diameter.

Choose from:

1. The Rufous Hummingbird
2. The Calliope Hummingbird
3. The Violet Crowned Hummingbird
4. The Ruby Throated Hummingbird
5. The Broad Billed Hummingbird
6. The Anna's Hummingbird

We only have 1 of each of these ones. 

*Please note the ring is for size comparison only

name: Vintage / Pink and Gold Matching Necklace and Brooch Set
description:
It's lovely to find matching sets in vintage items, usually they part ways over the years. This is a really pretty set comprising of a matching necklace and brooch.

Each piece has a pale pink stone set into the center, it is surrounded by a cream enamel and set into a gold tone metal.

The necklace chain is 20" long, the pendant is 2 cms tall, and the brooch is 4.3 wide. All are in great condition.

name: Vintage Style / Sterling Silver Dragonfly Necklace
description:
A lovely modern necklace in a bright silver, marked 925.

The pendant is a fine and delicate dragonfly. Approx 2.2 cms tall.

The chain is 18" long. In perfect condition.

name: Vintage / Mexican Silver Shell and Enamel Pendant Necklaces
description:
2 beautiful unusual necklaces. The pendants are made of Mexican silver and are inlaid with black enamel and iridescent shell pieces.

The left side necklace is an angular tear drop shape inlaid with a flower pattern, the shell in the one reflects pinks and yellow. Approx 4.6 cms tall and is in lovely condition.

The right side pendant is in a fan shape and inlaid with an abstract shell pattern, the shell in this one reflects turquoises and blue with a hint of pink. Approx 4.8 cms tall and is in lovely condition.

Both are on 18" necklace chains.

name: Vintage / Sterling Silver AA Milne Disney Necklaces
description:
A rare vintage set of AA Milne Winnie the Pooh Necklaces. 

Choose from Winnie the Pooh (complete with honey pot and honey bee charms), Tigger and Piglet.

All 3 necklaces and charms are sterling silver. The charms are 3D with detail all the way around. The chain is 18" long and marked 925.

Winnie the Pooh is 2.2 cms tall, Tigger is 2.3 cms tall and Piglet is 2 cms tall. 

Lovely dainty necklaces in great condition.

name: Vintage / Rhinestone Crystal Cocktail Bow Necklace
description:
Stunning sparkly vintage bow necklace, predicted 1950's. Super sparkly with lovely iridescent crystals and a beautiful bow design.

Looks lovely on, really glimmers and catches the light.

In lovely condition with no missing stones and just minor wear.

Approx 15" long plus a 2" extension, the bow dangles down a further 2".

name: Vintage Style / Sterling Silver Double Peacock Pearl Earrings
description:
Beautiful hook earrings with a hanging pearl design, each earring has two pearls. 

The pearls are 'petrol' purple/blue colour that reflects others colours, this colour of pearl are often fondly called peacock pearls.

Fully marked 925 on the hooks.

name: Vintage / Sterling Silver Viking Ship Nordic Ring
description:
A fantastic old sterling silver ring that depicts a viking sailing ship. The main picture is shouldered by a detailed knot design.

A really attractive and comfortable ring to wear. Fully marked 925 and in great condition.

Size O and a half/ P

name: Vintage / Sterling Silver Mare and Foal Necklace
description:
Vintage 1970's sterling silver necklace with a mare and foal pendant. 

A nicely detailed and larger size pendant. Completely 3D that shows the baby foal suckling from it's mum. Really lovely.

In great condition, the pendant is approx 2.1 cms tall. The chain is 20" long.

name: Vintage / Miracle Celtic Golden Thistle Brooch
description:
A beautiful vintage Miracle Celtic thistle brooch, the thistles are full of detail and set with large golden crystal stones. 

The metal is an antique gold tone in colour. The brooch is approx 4 x 3 cms in size and in perfect condition.

name: Vintage/ Sterling Silver Commemorative Queen Elizabeth Roses Necklace
description:
A stunning sterling silver necklace with a commemorative pendant for Queen Elizabeth.

The beautiful pendant depicts roses on each side, it is engraved on one side 'H.M Queen Elizabeth' and the other side 'The Queen Mother 4th August 1989'. 

The pendant itself is approx 3 cms tall and the chain is 20" long. In lovely condition.

name: Vintage / Pearl and Gold Bead Necklace
description:
An elegant white pearl and gold tone bead necklace. Strung together and bound with a gold tone clip clasp.

In lovely condition. Approx 17" long. Lightweight and comfortable to wear.

A great colour combination for dressing up with red and gold winter colours, or dressing down with pastel colours in spring.

name: Vintage Style / Jewellery Range Articulated Deer
description:
A bronze tone necklace with an articulated deer pendant. The deer himself is nice and big at 8.2 cms tall, and the chain he is on is 27" long.

Lovely to wear over a Christmas jumper!

name: Vintage Style / Sterling Silver Open Work Bangle
description:
Gorgeous open work bangle with a highly detailed filigree pattern, marked 925. 

The inner diameter is approx 7.5. In good condition.

name: Vintage / Golden Yellow and Orange Flower Necklace
description:
A fine 18" gold tone chain with an unusual metal flower pendant, the flower is also a gold tone and enhanced beautifully with white, yellow and orange enamel. This one looks quite old, possibly 50's/60's era.

The pendant itself is approx 3.7 cms tall and is in lovely condition.

name: Vintage / Crown Devon 'Dunkeld Hermitage' Preserve Jar
description:
A sweet little vintage preserve jar made by the company Crown Devon. 

The picture on this one depicts the beautiful scenic 'The Hermitage' in Dunkeld, Scotland. 

If you didn't want to use this one in the kitchen you could use it to keep trinkets in, it's very decorative so would even look nice just for display on a dresser.

The lid lifts off and has a small section cut away for a spoon to sit in. Approx 8.5 cms tall from base to top of lid. In good condition with just a tiny bit of age related glaze crackle.

name: Vintage / Golden Crystal and Pearl Brooch
description:
A beautiful old brooch, covered in sparkly golden crystal and a row of tiny white pearls.

Add a bit of vintage sparkle to any outfit!

Approx 3.1 cms in diameter and in good condition with just a little wear.

name: Vintage / Celtic 'Miracle' Chunky Medallion Necklace
description:
The company 'Miracle' are highly prized for their beautiful Celtic designs, with their vintage pieces being exceptionally desired and collectible.

This stunning necklace is features a large diamond shape antique gold tone pendant set with a striking orange and white glass stone.  Very fierce and strong in appearance.

The chain on this one is quite chunky and nice and long at 24" in length, the pendant itself is 4.3 cms tall. In great condition.

name: Vintage / Purple Pearl And Bead Necklace
description:
A gorgeous hue of deep mystic purple, this necklace is made up on a pearl beads and woven fabric beads. 

Approx 37" long. Wear this one over a cream jumper for a touch of festive colour. In lovely condition.

name: Vintage / Blue Flower Christian SlideLocket
description:
Highly unusual vintage locket. A antique gold tone with blue enamel flowers, the locket has a 'slide' opening rather than the usual book style opening.

When opened, on one side their is some kind of symbol or makers mark, and the other side their is a tiny picture of Jesus Christ. You could fix photos inside if desired.

The chain is approx 20" long and the locket itself approx 2.4 cms tall.

We haven't seen a necklace like this before and have struggled to find any history on it. A real little rarity.

name: Vintage / Sterling Silver Stylized Cat Earrings
description:
A pair of sterling silver earrings, quite large in size and shaped like cats. A quirky pair that would look quite elegant when worn.

Each cat is approx 5 cms in height. Fully hallmarked 925. In good condition with minor wear.

name: Vintage / Large Colourful Flower Chunky Necklace
description:
Lovely large flower pendant, set with deep pink and purple enamel and a pink center crystal. Approx 5cms in height.

Really unusual and attractive!

On a chunky 18" chain. In lovely condition.

name: Vintage / Sterling Silver Wishing Well Charm Necklace
description:
Great little vintage sterling silver necklace of a wishing well. This one is from the 60's/70's and although not hallmarked has been tested as sterling silver. 

The little well is just 2 cms high. the bucket inside the well even swings! The chain is 18" long and marked 925.

name: Vintage Style / Ornate Sugar Skull Necklace
description: Large bronze tone sugar skull necklace, the chain is 27" long

name: Vintage / Ornate Art Deco Style Cocktail Ring
description:
Lovely old ring in a silver tone with a mystic shimmery purple glass stone. 

The ornate design surrounding the glass is just gorgeous!

In good vintage condition with minor signs of wear. 

Adjustable in size, currently sitting at a size N - but would go down to around an I or up to a P.

name: Vintage / Damascene Pearl flower Brooch
description:
A vintage damascene flower brooch, set with pearls in the middle of the flowers. Gold, black and silver white tones that compliment each other so beautifully - damascene inlay work is quite an art.

Approx 6 cms in height. In great condition.

name: Vintage Style / Variety Of Sterling Silver Necklace
description:
3 beautiful sterling silver necklaces, each is on an 18" 925 chain.

The first (left side) is a long upside down diamond shaped with an ornate tip and turquoise stone inlay. Approx 3.1 cms tall and marked 925, in lovely condition.

The second (middle) is a fine filigree star necklace, it's very detailed for such a dainty pendant. Approx 2.1 cms tall and has been tested as sterling silver, in lovely condition.

The third (right side) is a beautiful Rennie Macintosh abstract flower. It is approx 2 cms tall and marked 925, in lovely condition.

name: Vintage / Snowdrop Flower Cameo Style Necklace
description:
Beautiful vintage necklace by Exquisite.

A large patterned frame with a blue and white snowdrop flower center. A larger size at 5.7 cms tall for the pendant and a 20" long chain.

In lovely condition.

name: Vintage / Dainty Pink Crystal and Pearl Dragonfly Brooch
description:
A dainty vintage brooch depicting a dragonfly. The eye are set with black crystals, the wings with pink crystals, and the body with silver pearls - all on a silver tone base.

Petite in size at approx 2.7 x 3.5 cms. In lovely condition with no tarnish.

name: Vintage / Polished Gemstone Panel Bracelet
description:
A great vintage bracelet made up of oval panels and links, every panel is set with a polished gemstone. We believe the gemstones include amethyst, tigers eye, and moss agate. 

So unusual, the colourful design is great to look at.

Approx 7.8" in length and in lovely condition.

name: Vintage Style / Hand Made Moon Owl Necklace
description:
This necklace is a design hand made by myself, it features a small pendant of an owl and moon silhouette, and is accented with a tiny pink pearl and purple crystal. 

A simple but sweet design that would be comfortable to wear every day.

The pendant is approx 3.8 cms tall including the bail clip, the chain is 18" long and platinum plated.

name: Vintage / Mexican Silver Crushed Turquoise Necklace
description:
Stunning necklace that consists of a Mexican silver pendant and 18ct white gold plated chain. 

So elegant, the pendant is long in design and fans out at the bottom. It is set with what looks like fragments of turquoise, which goes so beautifully with the silver.

The pendant is approx 6 cms tall and the chain is 18" long. In lovely condition.

name: Vintage Style / Cream Enamel Swallow Bird Necklace
description:
Pretty little rose gold tone and cream enamel swallow necklace. This is a modern one but so sweet, the swallow is carrying a little pearl.

The pendant is approx 5 cms tall and the chain is 19" long.

name: Vintage / Sterling Silver Penguin Necklace
description:
Adorable vintage sterling silver penguin necklace. this little guy is very cute with his little wings stretched out. He is hollow inside so nice and lightweight to wear.

He is approx 2.3 cms tall (he has been tested as sterling silver) and is on an 18" sterling silver chain. In lovely condition.

name: Vintage / Ceramic Dog Anubis Egyptian Necklace
description:
Highly unusual vintage necklace, this one has a silver tone metal frame with a ceramic plate set into it. The plate has lovely picture of a black dog tethered to a tree beside a river on it.

This one has a real Egyptian vibe to it, the black dog looks very much like Anubis.

Approx 3.3 cms tall for the pendant, and 20" in length for the chain. In lovely condition.

name: Vintage / Sterling Silver Pink Stone Ring
description:
A pretty sterling silver ring with an open work design and set with a marble effect pink stone. A lovely feminine piece.

Not hallmarked but positively tested as sterling silver. In good condition.

Size M

name: Vintage / Opal Style and Crystal Necklace
description:
A beautiful old necklace set with a pink/lilac/gold shimmery opal style stone, and surrounded by tiny crystals. Set in an antique gold metal. 

A really stunning necklace, sure to turn heads when worn! 

The pendant is approx 5.7 cms tall (including the bail) and the chain is 16" long. In lovely condition.

name: Vintage Style / Bird Cage Pocket Watch Necklace
description:
Silver tone pocket watch with vintage birdcage detail on the front. If you click the top, the panel comes down and the clock is inside, and a tiny mirror in the other half.

The clock is fully working and can be set using the toggle at the top. The back is plain silver tone.

The watch is 4.3 cms tall and the chain is 32".

name: Vintage Style / Jewellery Range Kitty Cat Locket Necklace
description:
Flowers and kitty cat locket, open and you can put a little trinket or photos inside. 


3.4 cms in height, on a 28" bronze tone chain.

name: Vintage Style / Jewellery Range Bronze Fairy Necklace
description: Elegant fairy necklace, 7.5cm in height in a bronze tone metal and adorned with crystals. On a 28" long chain.

name: Vintage Style / Jewellery Range Horses Pocket Watch Necklace
description:
Silver tone etched horse pocket watch. 31" long chain and the pendant is 4.4 cms high. 

Fully working with batteries and the time can be adjusted using the cog on the bottom.

name: Vintage Style / Jewellery Range Large Map Pocket Watch Necklace
description:
This is a larger style pocket watch necklace and has a vintage style explorer map pattern for the face (featuring Australia), the back is embossed with flowers. It is bronze tone (6 cm tall) and on a 32" long chain.

Fully working with batteries and the time can be adjusted using the cog at the top.

name: Vintage Style / Jewellery Range Cream Rose Necklace
description: 27" long chain with a bronze stem, leaves and cream rose flower

name: Vintage Style / Sterling Silver Gem Birds on a Branch Necklace
description:
Adorable 925 marked necklace with 3 cute little birds perched on a branch. Hanging from the branch are a red and purple crystal (if you just want one crystal we can remove one for you).

Such a sweet style. Approx 4.3 cms from one end of the branch to the other. The chain is 18" long.

name: Vintage / Sterling Silver and 9ct Gold Ankle Chains / Anklet
description:
2 gorgeous ankle chains / anklets.

The first is a shimmery twisted sterling silver design. It is simple and beautiful. Made of 925 Italian Sterling Silver, lovely quality and condition, approx 4.5" in length.

The second is a delicate 9ct gold chain with a tiny crystal cross charm. Fully hallmarked 375. Approx 5" in length, in lovely condition. A quality anklet.

These would be a great teamed with a pretty dress and high heels! Or sandals in the summer.

name: Vintage / 9ct Rolled Gold Engraved Bangle Bracelet
description:
Stunning old 9ct rolled gold bracelet. 

Engraved with a finely detailed filigree pattern the whole way round the petite 8 mm wide band. This one was made by the company Henry Griffith & Sons (Birmingham) in the early 1920's/30's. 

Approx 7.5" in diameter though does adjust to around 8" make it easier to put on. In good condition with minor wear, the bangle is not a perfect oval as it used to with a few minor dents, but still looks gorgeous on. 

A real little piece of vintage history to cherish.

name: Vintage / Silver Pearl Brooches
description:
2 beautiful vintage brooches.

Both of these ones have a focal point pearl. 

The brooch on the left side is an oval bar brooch which has three delicate hanging strands of silver ball beads. Approx 5.2 x 3.8 cms in size, in nice condition with minor signs of wear (the pin is a little bent on the back but still works just fine)

The brooch on the right is a floral daisy shape. It is set all the way around with tiny crystals. It's a great quality brooch with a a delicate safety chain attached. Approx 4.2 cms in diameter, and in lovely condition.

name: Vintage / Sterling Silver Bunny Rabbit Necklace
description:
This is a gorgeous 925 sterling silver (not marked, but tested as) vintage bunny rabbit charm on a sterling silver (925 marked) 20" chain.

The detail is so amazing for such a little charm (it is only 2.3 cms tall including the loop). This little bunny is so cute. I love how cheeky he looks with his front paw raised!

In lovely condition.

name: Vintage / Pink, Grey and Crystal Clear Bead Necklace
description:
A gorgeous chunky bead necklace made up of pale pink, metallic grey and crystal clear oval beads.

Very feminine and pretty! Approx 30" in length and in lovely condition.

name: Vintage Style / Jewellery Range Crystal Pegasus Necklace
description: Pegasus pendant on a ribbon and cord necklace, choose from different colours!

name: Vintage Style / Jewellery Range Floral Skull Necklace
description: Large statement wooden floral skull 7.5 cm tall pendant on a 30" silver tone chain

name: Vintage Style / Jewellery Range Wonderland Pocket Watch Necklace
description:
Bronze tone Wonderland pocket watch, with ornate cut out pattern including a bunny and a little key. 31" long chain and the pendant is 4.4 cms high. 

Fully working with batteries and the time can be adjusted using the cog on the top.

name: Vintage Style / Jewellery Range Little Owl Clock Necklace
description:
Bronze tone little barn owl clock necklace. 31" long chain and the pendant is 3.8 cms high. 

Fully working with batteries and the time can be adjusted using the cog on the bottom.

name: Vintage Style / Jewellery Range Lucky Swallow Bird Necklace
description: 16" + 2" extension) bronze tone chain with 'Lucky' enamel banner and swallow birds

name: Vintage Style / Jewellery Range Unicorn Necklace
description: 28" long bronze tone chain with an ornate unicorn and butterfly pendant

name: Vintage Style / Jewellery Range Enamel Bird Locket Necklace
description: 27" long bronze tone chain with a large enamel bird locket

name: Vintage Style / Jewellery Range Elephant Necklace
description: 28" long chain with a bronze ornate elephant pendant

name: Vintage Style / Jewellery Range Black Cat Necklace
description:
Enamel black and purple kitty cat necklace.

The chain is 27" long

name: Vintage Style / Jewellery Range Floral Deer Necklace
description: 27" long chain with a bronze filigree and flower deer pendant (approx 3" tall)

name: Vintage Style / Jewellery Range Galloping Horse Necklace
description: 27" long chain with antique silver and crystal rearing horse pendant (approx 2" tall)

name: Vintage Style / Jewellery Range Seahorse Necklace
description:
27" long chain with a bronze and enamel seahorse pendant (approx 3" tall)

Choose from red or green!

name: Vintage / Sterling Silver Channel Set Crystal Ring
description:
A lovely sterling silver vintage ring in a simple band design with channel set crystals. 

A simple and comfortable design, ideal for every day wear. Fully hallmarked 925.

This one does have a little wear in places reflective of its age, this is reflected in the price. Needless, it has plenty of life left and is still very beautiful.

Size R and a half/S

name: Vintage / Celtic Jasper Necklace
description:
A beautiful ornate Celtic style framed pendant with an earthy natural jasper stone center. 

The chain on this one is 24" and the pendant itself is 3.5 cms tall. It's in perfect condition.

name: Vintage / Sterling Silver Framed Rose Necklace
description:
Sweet sterling silver necklace with an oval frame and 3D rose flower hanging inside. Dainty with lovely details.

The pendant is approx 2.7 cms high and the chain is 14.5" long. Both are hallmarked 925.

name: Vintage / Cloisonne Bangle Bracelets
description:
3 stunning vintage cloisonne bangles. Cloisonne is a beautiful art consisting of detailed metalwork and enamel overlay.

You have a choice of blue, green or black based. Each has it's own original design and they vary in width, lovely to wear layered together or just as lovely individually.

name: Vintage Style / Chinese Zodiac Cuff Bangle
description:
A beautiful modern bangle that depicts the 12 zodiac star signs. The detail on all of the little animals is great, this bangle is lovely and unusual.

Due to the open ended cuff design, this bangle should fit most wrist sizes as it can be widened or squeezed tighter to suit.

name: Vintage / Sterling Silver 'Let The Band Play' Charm Necklace
description:
A quality sterling silver necklace which we have dubbed 'Let The Band Play' as the pendants on this one are a little trumpet and a little horn.

Lovely condition and the charms are originals from the 1970's. The charms are approx 2.2 cms in height and the chain is 18" long, all are sterling silver.

name: Vintage Style / Hand Made Christmas Earrings
description:
A selection of hand made Christmas earrings. Hand made by myself, I have only made one pair of each of these so they are extra special.

A choice of:

Red Holly Berries
Christmas Stockings
Holly Wreaths
Jingle Bells (that actually jingle) (top right)
Christmas Bells (bottom left)
Sleigh Ride
Frosty Snowflakes
Christmas Trees

All earrings are made with silver plated earrings wire so are lead and nickel free for allergy sufferers.

name: Vintage / Sterling Silver Giraffe Necklace
description: Lovely vintage sterling silver giraffe necklace. A dainty 18" link chain necklace with a sweet mini-giraffe just 2 cms tall. So cute!

name: Vintage Style / White Pearl and Crystal Bracelet
description:
Beautiful pearl and crystal wire bracelet. Perfect for the upcoming party season, the sparkly crystals combined with the white pearls is a classic and beautiful look.

This one is new, and will fit any wrist size due to the wire design.

name: Vintage Style / Mother of Pearl Star Necklace Gift box
description:
This little gift box contains a mother of pearl and crystal star necklace. Also in the gift box is a little scented candle, a home made bath bomb, and a home made bar of natural soap. 

The lid goes down and the box is finished off with a satin ribbon - the perfect gift!

name: Vintage / Ornate Flower and Crystal Ring
description:
Stunning vintage gold plated ring. The design of this one is breath taking, it's unusual and beautiful. In the middle is a tiny flower with a crystal center, surrounded by an ornate pattern of other smaller flowers and tiny little leaves. 

Size P / P and a half

In perfect condition. Expected to be from the 1970's era.

name: Vintage / Sterling Silver Welsh Dragon Necklace
description:
Magnificent vintage sterling silver Welsh Dragon necklace. This one is an absolute beauty, the dragon is perfectly detailed on such a small scale.

The necklace chain on this one is a solid sterling silver twist chain, both the necklace and pendant are weighty and excellent quality. The chain is hallmarked 925, the dragon is not hallmarked but has been positively tested as sterling silver.

name: Vintage Style / Custom Photo Dome Pendant Necklace
description:
Capture a special photograph and hold it with you forever with our bespoke dome pendant necklaces. 

These are completely hand made in a vintage style by myself. They can be made with your favourite wedding photo, a family photo, a pet - or any other you can think of! Available in silver tone, bronze tone, or gold tone metal.

Just email me your photo (to dearrosewithlove@gmail.com) and let me do the rest. Please let me know if you want the image printed in colour, black and white, or sepia.

Each necklace is just £7. If you don't want a photograph, we can also make these necklaces with a quote or message image which we can design for you for a little extra.

Custom pendants must be paid for up front but you will be emailed progress photos of your pendant being made to ensure you are happy with the outcome.

PHOTO ADVICE: The frame is an oval shape so I do recommend using a photo in a portrait position and where none of the main image is in the corners as they will be cut off.

Also, the better quality of photo that you select - the better quality the image will turn out in the pendant. I recommend selecting a high resolution image where possible. 

AFTERCARE: Please take care to not get your finished necklace wet. Dampness or submerging in water will result in damage to the image under the glass which we cannot be held responsible for. Please also avoid exposing your necklace to extreme temperatures as the glass may crack.
